Rating: 4
This pizza was great. I had no idea brie could melt so nicely and taste so good on pizza. We used whole wheat pizza dough which we stretched out into a crust. Used Gulden's Spicy Mustard.......the exact amount the recipe calls for. I imagine if you use too much the mustard could overwhelm the pizza but in our case it was perfect. Everything else was as directed. I blotted the tomatoes with paper towels to soak up some of the excess moisture. Delicious! And my husband loved it too.

